          "instruction": "Apply a² − b² = (a+b)(a−b)",
          "working": "49 − y² = 7² − y² = (7+y)(7−y)",
          "result": "(7 + y)(7 − y)",
          "voice_text": "49 minus y squared is a difference of squares. It equals 7 plus y times 7 minus y."
        }
      ],
      "trick_id": null,
